      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: auto-approve, needs-review + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'auto-approve' → Notion · ②→ Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)",
